        "body": "<p><code>RemoteWebDriver<\/code> accepts an <code>URL<\/code> as a parameter, but the URL from <code>java.net<\/code> package.<\/p>\n\n<p>Change \n<code>import com.gargoylesoftware.htmlunit.javascript.host.URL;<\/code><\/p>\n\n<p>to: <code>import java.net.URL<\/code><\/p>\n",
